title: Ep 133 - The New Decade
description: Todd, Digs, Nick, Connor, Ty, And Zito sit down to talk about the end of 2019 and all the awesome stuff that has come from it. They talk the best movies, tv show, inventions and moments to come from the last decade, and end the show with a CUSTOM Maraldo's Mad lib.
